<p><b>Is soroban good for kids?</b> Shen (2006) found that the soroban facilitates basic mathematical concept understanding in children who are cognitively challenged. In addition, it was also found to boost confidence in children and increase their interest in maths as a result (Foong, 1998; Shwalb, Sugie, & Yang, 2005).</p>
